==Trigonometry Book 1==
Book 1 is pre-calculus trigonometry.  We assume the student is relatively new to algebra and do algebra step by step.  

Many of the pages have closely related free/YouTube [[Trigonometry/Teachers_Notes/Khan_Academy_Videos|videos at the Khan Academy]].  This is by design.  Many students find the video presentation helpful with learning mathematical material.

As with all three trigonometry books, we have a "[[Trigonometry/For Enthusiasts/Introductions|for Enthusiasts]]{{stage|25%}}" section, which is for the student who finds the normal content and pace too slow and too easy, and yet still needs exercises and practice with Book 1 trigonometry.  

